# Contributing to All Emoji Fonts Project

We welcome contributions of new emoji fonts, bug fixes, and improvements!

## Adding a New Emoji Font

1. Place your font files in a new subdirectory under `fonts/<font-name>/`.
2. Include a CSS file to use the font on the web.
3. Add a `LICENSE` file for the font.
4. Update `README.md` with details about the font.

## Issues & Suggestions

- Open an issue describing missing emoji, font bugs, or feature requests.

Thanks for helping make emoji more accessible!
